{"tid":1993253,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"【愛情方程式】人妻送圍裙附數學題 丈夫計足4頁紙 答案原來...","createTime":"2020-04-28T15:47:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-30T03:25:53.000Z","uid":184679,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"736c8a829d8f38b746137fba1bf27458fa1c5c26","tid":1993253,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T15:47:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://statics.exmoo.com/uploads/2020-04-28/nDiBkPvN6nOYZn4QqdpT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatics.exmoo.com%2Fuploads%2F2020-04-28%2FnDiBkPvN6nOYZn4QqdpT.jpg&h=711c40eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（@shelfall twitter圖片）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n日本一名網民日前在Twitter分享夫妻之間的情趣驚喜，一名日本人妻送上一件圍裙，上面繡了一道數學題，他花了將近1個小時解題，結果發現畫出的圖竟是一個「大愛心」，讓他又驚又喜。Twitter一出隨即引發熱議，吸引超過50萬名網民朝聖，不少人直呼「根本是放閃文」。<br />\n<br />\n網民「@shelfall」在Twitter發文寫道，自己日前收到一件老婆送的圍裙，上面還附有一道親手縫製的數學題，而熱愛數學的他隨即埋首解題；經過近1小時的時間、算了滿滿4版紙，最後畫圖發現答案是一個愛心，讓他直呼「感受到老婆的愛」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://statics.exmoo.com/uploads/2020-04-28/Qs4ADUNBKnZOkC8sIEnE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatics.exmoo.com%2Fuploads%2F2020-04-28%2FQs4ADUNBKnZOkC8sIEnE.jpg&h=3cf43536&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://statics.exmoo.com/uploads/2020-04-28/ODvO3XUTSIG0MXycTwO0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatics.exmoo.com%2Fuploads%2F2020-04-28%2FODvO3XUTSIG0MXycTwO0.jpg&h=3ea7c3fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n貼文一出隨即吸引許多網民朝聖，「如果是我大概一輩子都算不出來」、「不僅考驗感情還考驗智商」、「理科的愛情」、「原來這就是真正的愛情方程式」；後來該網民「@shelfall」也分享老婆的圍裙，發現答案就在上面，讓不少人直呼「快被閃盲」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://statics.exmoo.com/uploads/2020-04-28/8Y2nUWpzsOsfEfY11f3v.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatics.exmoo.com%2Fuploads%2F2020-04-28%2F8Y2nUWpzsOsfEfY11f3v.jpg&h=abf787cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n妻子自己那件圍裙（左）原來繡有答案。（@shelfall twitter圖片）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.exmoo.com/article/147660.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.exmoo.com%2Farticle%2F147660.html&d=C0QxMr2ftqWfBh1dRblImNqeVONt7zbw7GHn8%2FjWPdo%3D&h=1d3fcf60\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.exmoo.com/article/147660.html</a>"},{"pid":"201dc127784e63340fd3e9650b7bd997dc0712d0","tid":1993253,"uid":105678,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T16:56:17.000Z","msg":"睇住答案傻鳩都識計啦，填number only<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"378523f7763670da75ed7d6cd7f2f28bcbb1613b","tid":1993253,"uid":36673,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"201dc127784e63340fd3e9650b7bd997dc0712d0","tid":1993253,"uid":105678,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T16:56:17.000Z","msg":"睇住答案傻鳩都識計啦，填number only<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T16:57:45.000Z","msg":"你咪唔浪漫囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 直男<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e1654cbc00301c9a01da3668e428f25e933f871","tid":1993253,"uid":35330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T17:04:49.000Z","msg":"睇到d數式先發現A Level都做過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96eb08296ee056b5fd2099210f8aaafe8182ef5b","tid":1993253,"uid":159913,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T17:05:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KCUn0Q8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKCUn0Q8.png&h=db6d8258&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n即時反應係用電腦計<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a23b2c9968986beb0ef454a516081b1c5a766708","tid":1993253,"uid":93141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T17:06:10.000Z","msg":"用電腦plot咪得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"151d5f73709872156c7b668a7b111eaaf2b68843","tid":1993253,"uid":61277,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T03:25:53.000Z","msg":"連登仔憑實力單身<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}